text: nạ̀n h̄æ la khụ̄x xạllxḥ̒ p̄hū̂ pĕn phracêā k̄hxng phwk cêā mị̀mī p̄hū̂ khwr dị̂ rạb kār kheārph s̄ạkkāra nxkcāk phraxngkh̒ p̄hū̂thrng bạngkeid thuks̄ìngthukxỳāng thèānận phwk cêā cng kheārph s̄ạkkāra phraxngkh̒ t̄heid læa phraxngkh̒ thrng pĕn p̄hū̂rạb mxbh̄māy h̄ı̂ khûmkhrxng rạks̄ʹā nı thuks̄ìngthukxỳāng
